  "or-bar-el": {
    "handle": "or-bar-el",
    "title": "Or Bar El",
    "body": "<p>Or Bar El is an independent creative from Tel Aviv. He studied animation at Bezalel Academy in Jerusalem and graduated in 2011 with a thesis film, <em>BEAT</em>, that went on to pick up awards and festival screenings.</p>\n<p>After co-founding the video content studio ONTHEBEACH and spending several years inside that world, he moved back toward the work that kept pulling harder: illustration, drawing, graffiti, and digital characters borrowed from everyday life. The animation background never really left. You can still feel it in the way the figures look like they might move a second after you stop looking.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/or_bar_el/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Instagram\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Instagram</a></p>",
    "bodySummary": "Or Bar El is a Tel Aviv illustrator and animator whose Bezalel training, film background, and years in video production still echo through his character-driven drawing practice.",
    "updatedAt": "2023-02-01T15:24:39Z"
  },
